DescUsage: <<
Additional functionality for bioperl (eg for maintaining a local database) can be 
obtained by installing the required perl modules before installing bioperl-pm. See
/sw/share/doc/bioperl-pm/INSTALL. Note that not all optional perl modules are 
available through fink.

All examples, docs, etc can be found in /sw/share/bioperl-pm/.
